      </li>
	  <li>
		<tale>AS_BoneForgingBreakthrough</tale>
        <label>Bone Forging</label>
        <minSeverity>6</minSeverity>
		<extraTooltip>Bones are hardened and forged to be able to withstand the forces imposed by further realms. Grants improved manipulation, breathing, blood filtration and blood pumping.</extraTooltip>
		<naturalHealingFactor>1.7</naturalHealingFactor>
		<painFactor>0.7</painFactor>
